name: Aikawa. Flash *SOLD OUT*
description:
Name: 
The Aikawa series is named after our amazingly creative friend. She keeps it vibrant and new.

We wanted to make pieces that screamed "I WANT SUMMER ALL YEAR ROUND". All the beads were assembled onto the head pins by hand.

Ingredients :
+neon colour glass beads
+gold brush chain 
+18 k plated clasp and chain

Production: Limited Run
Please note the beauty of hand-made:
Each piece will always be slightly different (custom orders are welcome)

Length: 42cm (approx.) when clasp closed.

name: Maryas. Yellow/Blue *SOLD OUT*
description:
Name:
The Maryas series is named after our dear friend who makes beauty seem effortless. 

Story:
All the beads in this series are from a vintage bead collection that was compiled by a collector in the 80s. The unknown collector sold  the treasure to an antique dealer (Rouge Gallery).  The entire collection was then bought and donated by a Numero Seis patron. Blessed. 

Ingredients : 
+18k gold plated chain
+hand-made glass beads (yellow and translucent blue)
+ribbed metal bead 

Production: 
1/1 (One of a kind)

Length: 
24cm when clasp closed.
